Abstract = {We examine the case of a lesson planning session within the context of
   professional development for dialogic instruction, and the lesson
   enacted following this session, which was intended to provide
   opportunities to 11th and 12th grade algebra students to explore
   polynomial functions in terms of their roots and linear factors. Our
