   relationship between epsilon and N, similar to the epsilon-N definition.
   By analyzing the students' responses to the validity of the statements
   as definitions of the limit of a sequence, students' understanding of
   such a relationship was classified into five major categories. This
   paper discusses some essential components that students must
   conceptualize in order properly to understand the relationship between e
